APT - Package Information

Use [prgm]apt show[/prgm] and [prgm]apt-cache[/prgm] to inspect packages.

$ [prgm]apt show[/prgm] [arg-value]package[/arg-value]                  # Show detailed package info
$ [prgm]apt-cache policy[/prgm] [arg-value]package[/arg-value]          # Show available versions and sources
